[normal]All of the proposals assume that the quality of advice provided to legal aid clients remains unchanged. In the case of solicitors in public family and immigration law, we believe more junior professionals are able to provide a sufficiently high quality ser
[normal]vice to enable individuals to be 
[normal]adequately represented should more senior solicitors take on less of this type of work. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We find this assumption concerning.
